org.archive.wayback

Interface ResultURIConverter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArchivalUrlContextResultURIConverterFactory.ArchivalUrlSpecialContextResultURIConverter, ArchivalUrlResultURIConverter, DomainPrefixResultURIConverter, ProxyHttpsResultURIConverter, RedirectResultURIConverter

    public interface ResultURIConverter
    Interface for implementations that convert a string datespec and URL into an absolute URL that will replay the specified URL at the specified date.
    Version:
    $Date$, $Revision$
    Author:
    brad
